---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const seo = {"title": "Teeth Whitening | D‑Essence Wellness", "description": "Brighter smiles with minimized sensitivity protocols.", "canonical": "/services/teeth-whitening", "type": "website", "ogImage": "/og-default" };
---

<BaseLayout {...seo}>

<section class="relative isolate paper">

<style is:global>
  :root{
    --paper:#F8F6F2; --ink:#141414; --muted:#5a5a5a; --rule:#E6E1D8;
  }
  .paper{ background:var(--paper); color:var(--ink); }
  .rule{ border-color:var(--rule); }
  .muted{ color:var(--muted); }
  .measure{ max-width: 64ch; }
  .dropcap:first-letter{ float:left; font-size:3.2rem; line-height:1; padding-right:.35rem; padding-top:.2rem; font-weight:600; }
  .ataglance{ display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:.75rem 1.25rem; font-size:.95rem; color:var(--muted); }
  .ataglance span::after{ content:"·"; margin-left:1.25rem; color:var(--muted); }
  .ataglance span:last-child::after{ content:""; margin:0; }
  .pullquote{ border-left:2px solid var(--ink); padding-left:.85rem; font-style:italic; color:#3b3b3b; margin: 1.25rem 0; }
  @media (max-width: 1023px){ .side-col{ display:none; } }
  details.faq summary{ list-style:none; }
  details.faq summary::-webkit-details-marker{ display:none; }
  .faq-toggle{ width:1.1rem; height:1.1rem; margin-right:.5rem; flex:0 0 auto; }
  details.faq[open] .plus{ display:none; }
  details.faq:not([open]) .minus{ display:none; }
  .icon-check{ width:1.1rem; height:1.1rem; flex:0 0 auto; margin-top:.15rem;}
  .timeline{ position:relative; }
  .timeline::before{ content:""; position:absolute; left:.9rem; top:.25rem; bottom:.25rem; width:2px; background:var(--rule); }
  .tl-step{ position:relative; padding-left:2.25rem; }
  .tl-badge{ position:absolute; left:0; top:.1rem; width:1.8rem; height:1.8rem; border-radius:999px; background:var(--ink); color:#fff; font-size:.9rem; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; font-weight:600; }
  .tl-title{ font-weight:600; }
</style>

  <!-- HERO (left‑aligned, no breadcrumb) -->
  <div class="px-6 pt-28 md:pt-32 pb-10">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl">
      <p class="text-xs tracking-wider uppercase muted text-center">Service</p>
      <h1 class="mt-2 text-[2.75rem] md:text-6xl leading-[1.05] font-semibold tracking-tight text-center">Teeth Whitening</h1>
<div class="mx-auto mt-8 h-px w-48 md:w-64 bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-black to-transparent"></div>

      
      
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- BODY -->
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 pb-24 grid grid-cols-12 gap-8">

    <!-- Removed left side labels entirely -->

    <!-- Main narrative -->
    <article class="col-span-12 lg:col-span-8 xl:col-span-7">
      <!-- DESCRIPTION (unique, professional) -->
      <section id="description" class="measure text-center">
        <p class="text-[18px] md:text-[20px] leading-[1.85] text-neutral-900 measure">
          This service focuses on refined, natural‑looking improvement. We begin with a focused consultation to understand your goals and medical background, map your features, and outline a plan that fits your timeline.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-[17px] md:text-[18px] leading-[1.85] text-neutral-800 measure">
          Technique, dosing, or device parameters are selected for your indication—always with clarity about what the service can and cannot accomplish, and when an alternative may be a better fit.
        </p>
        <ul class="service-attributes mt-6 flex flex-nowrap whitespace-nowrap items-center gap-1.5 sm:gap-2 md:gap-3 overflow-x-auto md:overflow-visible pr-1" role="list"><li class="shrink-0 whitespace-nowrap inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 md:gap-2 rounded-full border rule bg-white px-2 py-1 md:px-3 md:py-1.5 text-[11px] md:text-sm font-medium text-neutral-800 shadow-sm"><span class="rounded-full bg-neutral-900 h-1 w-1 md:h-1.5 md:w-1.5"></span>Comfort‑forward approach</li><li class="shrink-0 whitespace-nowrap inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 md:gap-2 rounded-full border rule bg-white px-2 py-1 md:px-3 md:py-1.5 text-[11px] md:text-sm font-medium text-neutral-800 shadow-sm"><span class="rounded-full bg-neutral-900 h-1 w-1 md:h-1.5 md:w-1.5"></span>Realistic timelines</li><li class="shrink-0 whitespace-nowrap inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 md:gap-2 rounded-full border rule bg-white px-2 py-1 md:px-3 md:py-1.5 text-[11px] md:text-sm font-medium text-neutral-800 shadow-sm"><span class="rounded-full bg-neutral-900 h-1 w-1 md:h-1.5 md:w-1.5"></span>Clear post‑care</li><li class="shrink-0 whitespace-nowrap inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 md:gap-2 rounded-full border rule bg-white px-2 py-1 md:px-3 md:py-1.5 text-[11px] md:text-sm font-medium text-neutral-800 shadow-sm"><span class="rounded-full bg-neutral-900 h-1 w-1 md:h-1.5 md:w-1.5"></span>Subtle, polished results</li></ul>
        <p class="mt-4 text-[17px] md:text-[18px] leading-[1.85] text-neutral-800 measure">“Less about changing your features, more about restoring ease and balance.”</p>
      </section>

      <div class="my-10 h-px border-t rule"></div>

      <!-- BENEFITS (unchanged from v2) -->
      <section id="benefits" class="measure">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Benefits</h2>
<div class="mt-4 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-x-10 gap-y-3">
  <div class="flex items-start gap-3 muted">
    <svg class="icon-check" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M20 7L10 17l-6-6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
    A measured, natural approach with clear guidance and realistic timelines.
  </div>
</div></section>

      <div class="my-10 h-px border-t rule"></div>

      <!-- THE PROCESS (unchanged from v2) -->
      <section id="process" class="measure">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight">The Process</h2>
        <div class="mt-4 timeline space-y-6">
          <div class="tl-step">
            <div class="tl-badge">1</div>
            <p class="tl-title">Consultation</p>
            <p class="muted mt-1">Goals, medical history, candidacy, and personalized plan.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="tl-step">
            <div class="tl-badge">2</div>
            <p class="tl-title">Treatment</p>
            <p class="muted mt-1">Technique and settings tailored to indication and area with comfort in mind.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="tl-step">
            <div class="tl-badge">3</div>
            <p class="muted tl-title">Review & Next Steps</p>
            <p class="muted mt-1">What to expect as results evolve; maintenance when helpful.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <div class="my-10 h-px border-t rule"></div>

      <!-- PRE / POST (unchanged from v2) -->
      <section id="care" class="measure">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Pre and Post‑Treatment Instructions</h2>
        <div class="mt-4 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-10">
          <div>
            <p class="font-medium">Before your visit</p>
            <div class="mt-2 pl-3 border-l-2" style="border-color: currentColor;">
              <ul class="list-none space-y-2 muted">
                <li>• Avoid new actives/irritants if directed.</li>
                <li>• Disclose medications, allergies, and recent procedures.</li>
                <li>• Hydrate and arrive with clean skin.</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-medium">After your visit</p>
            <div class="mt-2 pl-3 border-l-2" style="border-color: currentColor;">
              <ul class="list-none space-y-2 muted">
                <li>• Follow your specific post‑care steps.</li>
                <li>• Protect from heat/sun and pause harsh actives.</li>
                <li>• Contact us if unexpected reactions occur.</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <div class="my-10 h-px border-t rule"></div>

      <!-- FAQs (unchanged from v2) -->
      <section id="faqs" class="measure">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        <div class="mt-4 space-y-3">
          <details class="faq">
            <summary class="flex items-center cursor-pointer">
              <svg class="faq-toggle plus" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M12 5v14M5 12h14" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
              <svg class="faq-toggle minus" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M5 12h14" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
              <span class="font-medium ml-1">How many sessions will I need?</span>
            </summary>
            <p class="muted mt-2 ml-6">It depends on indication, area, and your goals. We outline an initial and maintenance plan during your consultation.</p>
          </details>
          <details class="faq">
            <summary class="flex items-center cursor-pointer">
              <svg class="faq-toggle plus" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M12 5v14M5 12h14" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
              <svg class="faq-toggle minus" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M5 12h14" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
              <span class="font-medium ml-1">Will it look natural?</span>
            </summary>
            <p class="muted mt-2 ml-6">We favor harmony and restraint for results that feel like you on a good day.</p>
          </details>
          <details class="faq">
            <summary class="flex items-center cursor-pointer">
              <svg class="faq-toggle plus" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M12 5v14M5 12h14" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
              <svg class="faq-toggle minus" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M5 12h14" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
              <span class="font-medium ml-1">Is there downtime?</span>
            </summary>
            <p class="muted mt-2 ml-6">Most services have minimal downtime; we provide specifics and simple aftercare to follow.</p>
          </details>
          <p class="text-sm muted">*Informational content only; not medical advice. Individual results vary.</p>
        </div>
      </section>
    </article>

    <!-- Right margin notes (sticky cues) remain -->
    <aside class="side-col col-span-2 lg:col-span-3 xl:col-span-4">
      <div class="sticky-top measure">
        <p class="muted"><strong>Good to know:</strong> Technique, cadence, and aftercare are tailored to your timeline.</p>
        <p class="muted mt-4"><strong>Quality:</strong> Trained providers, premium sourcing, evidence‑informed protocols.</p>
        <p class="muted mt-4"><strong>Expectations:</strong> Realistic timelines and clear check‑ins.</p>
      </div>
    </aside>
  </div>
</section>

</BaseLayout>
